import React from "react"; import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom"; import Header from '../Header/Header.js' import Title from '../Title/Title.js' import active from '../img/active.png' import archive from '../img/archive.png' import test from '../img/test.png' import dp from '../img/dp.jpg' import CalendarHeatmap from "react-calendar-heatmap"; import { UserAuth } from '../../context/AuthContext' const Analytics = () => { const {user} = UserAuth() return (
<div className="achievements-container"> <div className="side-col"> <h3>Account details</h3> <img className="profile-pic" src={dp}></img> <p>Email: {user.email}</p> <p>Level: 1</p> </div> <div className="test1"> <h3>Dashboard</h3> <CalendarHeatmap className="activity-calendar" startDate={new Date('2021-12-31')} endDate={new Date('2022-12-31')} values={[ { date: '2016-01-01', count: 12 }, { date: '2016-01-22', count: 122 }, { date: '2016-01-30', count: 38 }, ]} /> <h3>Mood Journals</h3> <div className='side-col-books'> <NavLink className='side-col-links' to='/archived-thoughts'> <img className='side-col-img' src={archive}></img> </NavLink> <NavLink className='side-col-links' to='/active-thoughts'> <img className='side-col-img' src={active}></img> </NavLink> </div> <div className="side-col-links-container"> <NavLink className='side-col-links' to='/journal'> Create New Mood Journal Entry </NavLink> </div> </div> </div> </div> ) } export default Analytics
